guardian-api.name: auditor
guardian-api.description: This role has read only access to user management and read access to assigned projects.

guardian-api.name: pentester
guardian-api.description: This role can read and modify the projects he has access to but cannot delete them.

guardian-api.name: customer
guardian-api.description: This role can read the projects he has access to but cannot modify or delete them.

guardian-api.name: manager
guardian-api.description: This role can create and read or projects but cannot delete projects. In addition, this role can modify project metadata but not pentest results.

guardian-api.name: supertester
guardian-api.description: Like role pentester, but he can also manage Test Items and Test Catalogs.

guardian-api.name: admin
guardian-api.description: This role has the highest privileges and is allowed to do anything.
